<plot>Lily, a young girl who's mother's constant drinking and partying drives them apart, decides to find her father, when she finds a picture of him in the house one day. Behind her mother's back, Lily tracks down the one man who might be able to give her a good life, and even catches a glimpse of him. But Lily's mother figures out that Lily no longer wants to live with her, and it drives her to a place which changes everything for both of them.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?336800</url></doc>
